box": [110.4, 844.3, 234.4, 870.3]}, {"text": ">1", "bbox": [486.1, 847.2, 508.3, 870.3]}, {"text": "1", "bbox": [608.3, 847.2, 618.8, 870.3]}, {"text": ">1", "bbox": [707.0, 847.2, 729.1, 870.3]}, {"text": "________________________________", "bbox": [104.2, 878.3, 304.2, 892.2]}, {"text": "(*)  DSO and book-to-bill are for the fourth quarter ended 2012, 2011, and 2010.", "bbox": [104.2, 892.6, 721.0, 916.0]}, {"text": "•", "bbox": [141.7, 940.9, 154.2, 964.0]}, {"text": "Net Revenues: Our net revenue decreased in our EMEA and APAC regions, offset by an increase in the Americas", "bbox": [179.2, 940.9, 1125.6, 964.0]}, {"text": "region in 2012, compared to 2011. By market, we experienced declines in both service provider and enterprise markets", "bbox": [179.2, 965.9, 1175.3, 989.0]}, {"text": "in 2012, compared to 2011. The year-over-year decrease in our net revenues during 2012 was primarily due to a", "bbox": [179.2, 990.9, 1116.1, 1014.0]}, {"text": "decline in sales of our core and edge legacy routing products and firewall products, partially offset by increases in our", "bbox": [179.2, 1015.9, 1166.3, 1039.0]}, {"text": "service revenue, switching products, and high-end SRX products.", "bbox": [179.2, 1040.9, 725.4, 1064.0]}, {"text": "•", "bbox": [141.7, 1090.9, 154.2, 1114.0]}, {"text": "Gross Margin: Our gross margin as a percentage of revenues decreased in 2012, compared to 2011, due to lower", "bbox": [179.2, 1090.9, 1122.4, 1114.0]}, {"text": "product margin from $44.3 million in inventory charges related to component inventory held in excess of forecasted", "bbox": [179.2, 1115.9, 1151.6, 1139.0]}, {"text": "demand and an intangible asset impairment charge of $16.1 million, and to a lesser extent, due to an increase in the", "bbox": [179.2, 1140.9, 1143.9, 1164.0]}, {"text": "size and number of strategic contracts with lower margins, and a shift in product mix to lower margin products. This", "bbox": [179.2, 1165.9, 1153.5, 1189.0]}, {"text": "decrease was partially offset by an increase in service margin.", "bbox": [179.2, 1190.9, 699.6, 1214.0]}, {"text": "•", "bbox": [141.7, 1240.9, 154.2, 1264.0]}, {"text": "Operating Income: Our operating income as a percentage of revenues decreased in 2012, compared to 2011, primarily", "bbox": [179.2, 1240.9, 1169.4, 1264.0]}, {"text": "due to slower revenue growth relative to our sales and marketing and research and development expense, as we", "bbox": [179.2, 1265.9, 1112.4, 1289.0]}, {"text": "continue to invest in our innovative portfolio and bring new products to market. In addition, restructuring and other", "bbox": [179.2, 1290.9, 1145.5, 1314.0]}, {"text": "associated charges of $99.7 million were recorded in 2012, related to workforce reduction activities, facility closures,", "bbox": [179.2, 1315.9, 1162.4, 1339.0]}, {"text": "asset impairment charges, and contract terminations.", "bbox": [179.2, 1340.9, 616.8, 1364.0]}, {"text": "•", "bbox": [141.7, 1390.9, 154.2, 1414.0]}, {"text": "Net Income Attributable to Juniper Networks and Net Income Per Share Attributable to Juniper Networks Common", "bbox": [179.2, 1390.9, 1145.1, 1414.0]}, {"text": "Stockholders: The decrease in net income attributable to Juniper Networks in 2012, compared to 2011, reflects the", "bbox": [179.2, 1415.9, 1136.6, 1439.0]}, {"text": "lower operating income discussed above.", "bbox": [179.2, 1440.9, 522.3, 1464.0]}, {"text": "•", "bbox": [141.7, 1484.7, 154.2, 1507.7]}, {"text": "Operating Cash Flows: Operating cash flows decreased in 2012, compared to 2011, primarily due to lower net", "bbox": [179.2, 1484.7, 1107.0, 1507.7]}, {"text": "income, higher taxes paid, timing of payments to our vendors, and a decrease in deferred revenue, offset by collections", "bbox": [179.2, 1509.7, 1174.4, 1532.7]}, {"text": "of our outstanding receivables.", "bbox": [179.2, 1534.7, 436.1, 1557.7]}, {"text": "Table of Contents", "bbox": [104.2, 21.9, 252.0, 44.9]}]}